```json
{
  "key": "photos/YYYY-MM-DD/<uuid>_filename.ext",
  "bucket": "factoryflow",
  "mimeType": "image/jpeg|image/png|image/webp",
  "size": 12345
}
```

**Important:** that `key` is what you store in PHOTO answer value.

