# Conclusion: “which API is used when”

### Login (everyone)

* `POST /auth/login`

### Admin setup

* `POST /plants` (create plant)
* `POST /users/managers` (create manager)
* `GET /users` / `PATCH /users/{id}` / enable/disable

### Form lifecycle (admin)

* `POST /forms` or `POST /forms/import` → create DRAFT
* `PATCH /forms/{id}` → edit while DRAFT
* `POST /forms/{id}/publish` → publish
* `POST /forms/{id}/clone` → create new version as DRAFT
* `POST /forms/{id}/archive` → archive published
* `GET /forms` / `GET /forms/{id}` → view

### Mobile usage (user)

* `GET /mobile/forms?plantId=...` → list published templates
* `POST /files/upload?folder=photos` → upload photo (if PHOTO field)
* `POST /mobile/forms/submissions` → submit filled form
* `GET /mobile/forms/submissions/mine` → view my submissions
* `GET /files/signed-url?key=photos/...` → view photo

### Review (manager/admin)

* `GET /mobile/forms/submissions` → list submissions to review
* `GET /mobile/forms/submissions/{id}` → open detail
* `POST /mobile/forms/submissions/{id}/approve` → approve
* `POST /mobile/forms/submissions/{id}/reject` → reject with reason

### Dashboard (admin/manager)

* All `/dashboard/*` endpoints for analytics widgets

### Ops/Debug

* `GET /health`

